| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3063 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c28d0a75-59ad-5a50-8f4f-966de5a29c6d"
